org.alljoyn.onboarding

Interface OnboardingService


  • public interface OnboardingService
    An interface for both Onboarding client (onboarder) and server (onboardee).

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  OnboardingService.AuthType
      Enumeration of authentication types -3 - wpa2_auto, onboardee should try WPA2_TKIP and WPA2_CCMP -2 - wpa_auto, onboardee should try WPA_TKIP and WPA_CCMP -1 - any, The onboardee chooses the authentication 0 - Open Personal AP is open 1 - WEP 2 - WPA_TKIP 3 - WPA_CCMP 4 - WPA2_TKIP 5 - WPA2_CCMP 6 - WPSS
      static class  OnboardingService.OnboardingState
      Enumeration of onboarding state 0 - Personal AP Not Configured 1 - Personal AP Configured/Not Validated 2 - Personal AP Configured/Validating 3 - Personal AP Configured/Validated 4 - Personal AP Configured/Error 5 - Personal AP Configured/Retry
